cs.SY, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.OH 

This paper deals with online control of systems, which is a subfield of control theory. Therefore, cs.SY (Systems and Control) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also uses tools from online optimization, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also deals with robotics, which falls under cs.RO (Robotics and Automation). Finally, the paper deals with optimization algorithms, which falls under cs.OH (Optimization and Control).
